OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FThe number of battery-related fires
OL,8,Fhas reached 'epidemic levels',
OL,9,Faccording to disposal company Biffa.
OL,11,FThey've increased by 70% in the last
OL,12,Ffour years - causing more than one
OL,13,Fbillion pounds worth of damage
OL,14,Fannually.
OL,16,FWaste disposal services in West Sussex
OL,17,Fare reporting daily fires at their
OL,18,Ffacilities, which it believes are
OL,19,Flikely caused by batteries inside
OL,20,Fitems such as vapes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
