PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FThey usually contain lithium-ion
OL,8,Fbatteries which can ignite and explode
OL,9,Fif they are pierced.
OL,11,FPeople are being reminded to make sure
OL,12,Fthey dispose of them responsibly.
OL,14,FIndependent organisation Material
OL,15,FFocus also found 6.3 million vapes and
OL,16,Fpods are being thrown away every week
OL,17,Fdespite the single-use vape ban.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FScott Butler, Executive Director,
OL,8,FMaterial Focus said: "The vapocalypse
OL,9,Fcontinues, as we see a rise in battery
OL,10,Ffires in bin lorries and at waste and
OL,11,Frecycling centres across the UK.
OL,13,F"The single-use vapes ban has had an
OL,14,Fimpact, but 6 million vapes and pods
OL,15,Fare still being thrown away a week and
OL,16,Fthis is still a massive waste of
OL,17,Fvaluable materials and a major fire
OL,18,Frisk.
OL,26,@pD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
