OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,F"A new tobacco and vapes bill is
OL,8,Fprogressing through parliament - the
OL,9,Fbill proposes that the sellers of
OL,10,Fvapes will need to be licensed to do
OL,11,Fthis, similar to those who sell
OL,12,Ftobacco and alcohol.
OL,14,F"Requiring these licensed premises to
OL,15,Falso offer takeback and communicate
OL,16,Fthis clearly to their customers could
OL,17,Fhave a big impact.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,F"It should be as easy to recycle a
OL,8,Fvape as it is to buy one. We want more
OL,9,Fvapers demanding that the places where
OL,10,Fthey buy them also provide recycling
OL,11,Fpoints.
OL,13,F"It is a long-standing legal
OL,14,Fobligation for all of the stores who
OL,15,Fare profiting from selling them must
OL,16,Foffer safe recycling drop-off points
OL,17,Fand cover the costs of doing that.
OL,19,F"Vape producers and importers should
OL,20,Fthen cover the costs of recycling."
OL,26,@oD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FBut there is concern at how often
OL,8,Ffires caused by batteries are
OL,9,Fhappening.
OL,11,FIn the last year there's been over
OL,12,F1,200 blazes - caused by vapes and
OL,13,Felectricals with hidden batteries in
OL,14,Fbin lorries or waste sites.
OL,16,FThat's compared to 700 four years ago.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
