OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FGareth Rollings, Head of Waste at West
OL,8,FSussex County Council said: "A fire in
OL,9,Fa refuse truck means potentially the
OL,10,Ftruck needs to be tipped out on the
OL,11,Froadside, which obviously causes
OL,12,Fproblems for the public who then can't
OL,13,Fuse that road.
OL,15,F"Then at our end disposable point
OL,16,Fwhere we are actually processing
OL,17,Fwaste, that leads us to having quite a
OL,18,Flot of fires, which then impacts on
OL,19,Fthe staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
