PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1774937073
OL,3,C'Epidemic' of battery-related fires
OL,4,Cprompts warning over correct vape
OL,5,Cdisposal
OL,7,FAccording to new figures, nearly half
OL,8,Fof vape users said they didn't know
OL,9,Fthey could recycle them, either by
OL,10,Fputting them in bins at local
OL,11,Fhousehold recycling sites or the
OL,12,Fdesignated recycle bins at many vape
OL,13,Fshops.
OL,15,FA new Tobacco and Vapes Bill is
OL,16,Fprogressing through Parliament, which
OL,17,Faims to make it as easy to recycle a
OL,18,Fvape, as it is to buy one.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
